Class PotionHandler

java.lang.Object
com.vk2gpz.tokenenchant.api.EnchantHandler
com.vk2gpz.tokenenchant.api.PotionHandler
All Implemented Interfaces:
CEHandler, EventMapper, org.bukkit.command.CommandExecutor, org.bukkit.command.TabCompleter, org.bukkit.command.TabExecutor, org.bukkit.event.Listener
public abstract class PotionHandler extends EnchantHandler
PotionHandler is used to implement a custom enchant which will NOT be registered with Minecraft's Enchantment system althorugh it extends EnchantHandler. Hence, it rely on its identity displayed on ItemStack's lore.
